        {
            "title": "天文台｜部分地區能見度較低 日間炎熱及非常乾燥 最高氣溫約29度",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"黎志偉攝\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/6e1d87045a0e439ca9034b9829586962/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250415/_2025041506502969838.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">黎志偉攝</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>廣東地區天色大致良好。同時，受乾燥的大陸氣流及沙塵天氣影響，廣東部分地區能見度較低。\n\n</p>\n<p>本港地區今日天氣預測，大致天晴，但部分地區能見度較低。日間炎熱及非常乾燥，最高氣溫約29度。吹微風。\n\n</p>\n<p>展望明日大致天晴及乾燥，初時能見度較低。本週後期漸轉潮濕，日間炎熱，亦有幾陣驟雨。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4195466/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"分區氣溫\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/df3a774e6cb6b17bf7c239f0a7c8755d/2025-04/2025-04-15_06_16_18.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        分區氣溫\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4195467/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"九天天氣預報\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/eb23d31e26456529f381a7a7d1fdc53d/2025-04/2025-04-15_06_19_18.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        九天天氣預報\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4195468/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"部分地區能見度較低。黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/81853f9479ea8267ef83a09aefaa32c1/2025-04/KakaoTalk_Photo_2025-04-15-06-11-06_003.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        部分地區能見度較低。黎志偉攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4195469/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"日間炎熱及非常乾燥。黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6c0a0aa4e0a1dd04fd1408e3dd8b04ae/2025-04/KakaoTalk_Photo_2025-04-15-06-11-10_004.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        日間炎熱及非常乾燥。黎志偉攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4195470/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"最高氣溫約29度。黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8d775a9051822e88bae83fd1abbf6618/2025-04/KakaoTalk_Photo_2025-04-15-06-11-13_005.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        最高氣溫約29度。黎志偉攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>受非常乾燥的大陸氣流及沙塵天氣影響，加上風勢微弱，廣東地區今明兩日能見度仍然較低，日夜溫差頗大。預料一股偏南氣流會在隨後兩三日逐漸影響沿岸地區，該區天氣較為潮濕。而一道低壓槽會在本週後期至下週初為廣東帶來驟雨。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2063979/即時-港聞-天文台-部分地區能見度較低-日間炎熱及非常乾燥-最高氣溫約29度",
